OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,FThe Duke of Cornwall, Prince William
OL,8,Fhas been visiting the Duchy on St
OL,9,FPiran's Day to honour some of the the
OL,10,Funsung heroes of Storm Goretti.
OL,12,FFirefighters in Helston were amongst
OL,13,Fthose to meet the Duke, as he toured
OL,14,Fthe area to hear how communities
OL,15,Frallied together in the wake of the
OL,16,Fferocious storm on January 8th.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
