CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772824283
OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,FHelston was hit particularly hard hit
OL,8,Fby the storm which brought down power
OL,9,Fliens, felled thousands of trees and
OL,10,Fclaimed the life of a resident in
OL,11,Fnearby Mawgan.
OL,13,FPart of the visit included discussions
OL,14,Fwith senior leaders and responders to
OL,15,Freflect on lessons
OL,17,Flearned from the storm and ways to
OL,18,Ffuture proof and strengthen Cornish
OL,19,Fcommunities in the face of extreme
OL,20,Fweather.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772824283
OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,FThe Duke also visited the award
OL,8,Fwinning Gear Farm pasty company on the
OL,9,FLizard. Thanks to a generator the
OL,10,Ffamily were able to continue serving
OL,11,Flocal residents who were without
OL,12,Fessential services for days after the
OL,13,Fstorm.
OL,15,FIn celebration of his visit the Duke
OL,16,Fplanted a tree in a new woodland area
OL,17,Fbeing created on the farm.
OL,19,FHe also enjoyed a prize-winning pasty
OL,20,Fand had a go at making one, as well as
OL,21,Fhelping to take orders over the phone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772824283
OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,FJosie Trounson from Mullion was one of
OL,8,Fthe customers who ordered from the
OL,9,FDuke, and says she thought he "did a
OL,10,Fvery good job".
OL,12,F"We've got five children 'up country'
OL,13,Fand our daughter is coming down and I
OL,14,Fthought we'd have pasties for all of
OL,15,Fthem because all of our children love
OL,16,Fpasties and Gear Farm is where we
OL,17,Falways go.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772824283
OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,F"I telephoned to order them and it was
OL,8,Fquite noisy when I called. I asked
OL,9,Fhave you got plenty of fresh pasties
OL,10,Fand I'd also like ten frozen ones.
OL,12,F"Then they asked me what my name was
OL,13,Fand I said 'Josie', and they said
OL,14,F'Juicy?'
OL,16,F"Prince William did a very good job. I
OL,17,Fdidn't realise while I was on the
OL,18,Ftelephone - I did think it was rather
OL,19,Fnoisy and thought it was because of St
OL,20,FPiran's Day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1772824283
OL,3,CThe Duke of Cornwall's visit
OL,4,Chighlights those who responded during
OL,5,CStorm Goretti
OL,7,F"When I arrived they asked my name and
OL,8,FI said 'Josie, but you thought it was
OL,9,FJuicy!' They asked if I knew who took
OL,10,Fmy order and they said it was Prince
OL,11,FWilliam and I was flabbergasted.
OL,13,F"We ate the pasties before we left the
OL,14,Ffarm!
OL,16,F"My Daughter in law sent me a text and
OL,17,Fsaid not only have you got a celebrity
OL,18,Ffriend but you've got a new name!"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
